http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/Passport-inquiry-now-in-just-five-days-says-SP/article13988312.ece

The period for inquiry of candidates who are seeking passport has now been reduced from 21 days in the past to five days and for job inquiry to three days. And it is made possible with the launch of police websitewww.vzmpolice.com.At a press conference on Thursday, Superintendent of Police Navdeep Singh Grewal said that the passport verification could be done hereafter online within five days and job inquiry in three days.The step taken in this regard would help issue passports in time to the candidates, he added.The police official also presented details of other services offered online.